00:10:04.150 --> 00:10:06.240
und niemand kommt lebend heraus.

00:10:06.240 --> 00:10:07.120
Ich verstehe,

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:08.390
Chef.

00:10:10.030 --> 00:10:11.390
